                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_PcEMT3"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_nL9mgY": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Will My Dress Be Customised To My Measurements?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_NTz9y7": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Yes MWL By You custom styles are customised to your measurements.<br/><br/>Unlike most bridal brands, we don't rely on a single standard size across your entire gown. Instead, we take individual measurements for your bust, waist, and hips, and tailor each section of the gown to those exact proportions. This means no unnecessary alternations, no compromising on fit, and no stress; just a gown that feels like it was made for you, because it was.<br/><br/>Thanks to our own production house, we can offer this level of precision and care as part of our standard service - something most brands simply can't match. It's just one of the ways we make sure every Made With Love gown lives up to its name.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_NTz9y7"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_amkLhB": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "How Long Will It Take For My Dress To Be Made?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_WLU8Fi": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>MWL By You custom dresses have the same production & lead times as all MWL styles. Consult with one of our bridal stylists today to query your bridal timelines or contact our Customer Care team <a href=\"/pages/contact\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Contact\">here</a>.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
